# REST Client requests for the Cost Estimator API
# Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client):
#   - Click "Send Request" above any request below.
# Switch @baseUrl between the deployed API Gateway and your local dev server.

# --- Deployed API Gateway (eu-west-2, stage: prod) ---
@baseUrl = https://2lg6zp5x78.execute-api.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/prod

# --- Local Express dev server (npm run dev) ---
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Estimate costs
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/estimate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestsPerMonth": 1000000,
  "averageRequestDurationMs": 200,
  "averageMemoryMb": 256,
  "region": "eu-west-2",
  "apiGatewayType": "REST"
}

### Estimate chart data
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/estimate/chart
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "averageRequestDurationMs": 200,
  "averageMemoryMb": 256,
  "region": "eu-west-2",
  "apiGatewayType": "REST",
  "minRequestsPerMonth": 10000,
  "maxRequestsPerMonth": 100000000,
  "dataPoints": 20
}
